## TocParameters.injectedStyleId property

If `indicator` is not `false`<!-- -->, an inline style tag is injected to `<head>`<!-- -->. This is the id of that style tag. Defaults to `toc-style`

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
injectedStyleId: string;
```
